&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead end-to-end execution of automation lifecycle and obsolescence projects, including PLC, HMI (PanelView), SCADA, and controls system upgrades&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage projects ranging from minor firmware updates to full-scale control system replacements, including planning, budgeting, scheduling, and execution&lt;/li&gt;
